div><div class="flex flex-col px-[14px] md:px-0"><div class="mb-[24px] block md:hidden"><h1 class="text-bg_opacity_100 mb-[12px] text-[24px] font-[500]">春天里</h1><div class="scroll-shadow-wrapper"><div class="scroll-shadow-content hide-scrollbar max-h-[88px] overflow-y-auto" data-top-scroll="false" data-bottom-scroll="true"><p class="text-text_01 text-[14px] leading-[22px]">风格：汪峰式流行摇滚，沧桑沙哑男声，中速 120BPM，情绪励志、走心、坚持、温暖、力量感
配器：电吉他、钢琴、弦乐、鼓、贝斯，编曲饱满有层次，副歌爆发感强
人声：成熟男声，沙哑有故事感，像汪峰那种呐喊又深情的唱法, 新世纪</p></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col"><div class="mb-[8px] flex items-center gap-[10px]"><div class="h-[20px] w-[20px] overflow-hidden rounded-full md:h-[24px] md:w-[24px]"><img alt="user_avatar" referrerPolicy="no-referrer" crossorigin="anonymous" loading="lazy" width="24" height="24" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-full" style="color:transparent" src="https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/PiajxSqBRaEKJn2qtYBoFvO7bRf2OgAyERcibFKqKZPDhgx8HwSsQ4ZWTJvXGiawYVtzMQYoia3BlI1Fia0SFY6C7Q9iaRU1nXDY5TFuzef20icyGiaXmQgjnXpx3A/132"/></div><span class="text-text_01 text-[12px] font-[600] md:text-[15px]">朗月清风</span></div><span class="text-bg_opacity_60 mb-[12px] block text-[10px] font-[400] md:mb-[32px] md:text-[12px]">2026-03-08 15:59</span><div class="flex items-center gap-[28px]"><div><div><div class="ant-dropdown-trigger cursor-pointer text-text_00 h-[28px] w-[28px]"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M14.3984 15.6001H5.59844" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"></path><path d="M10.0399 3.61636V12.0164M10.0399 12.0164L14 8.05617M10.0399 12.0164L6.03385 8.01034" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class="text-text_00  flex h-[28px] w-[28px] items-center justify-center rounded-[4px] transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110  cursor-pointer"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M4.89844 4.81225V16.4368C4.89844 16.7128 5.16778 16.9084 5.43022 16.823L9.8011 15.4008C10.0461 15.3211 10.31 15.3211 10.555 15.4008L14.9259 16.823C15.1883 16.9084 15.4577 16.7128 15.4577 16.4368V4.81225C15.4577 4.36366 15.094 4 14.6454 4H5.71069C5.26209 4 4.89844 4.36366 4.89844 4.81225Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="text-text_00  flex h-[28px] w-[28px] items-center justify-center rounded-[4px] transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110  cursor-pointer"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M22.4 13.9996C22.4 11.7718 21.515 9.63522 19.9397 8.05991C18.3644 6.48461 16.2278 5.59961 14 5.59961C11.6517 5.60844 9.39771 6.52475 7.70934 8.15694L5.60001 10.2663" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.86667" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M5.60001 5.59961V10.2663H10.2667M5.60001 13.9996C5.60001 16.2274 6.485 18.364 8.06031 19.9393C9.63561 21.5146 11.7722 22.3996 14 22.3996C16.3483 22.3908 18.6023 21.4745 20.2907 19.8423L22.4 17.7329" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.86667" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><path d="M17.7333 17.7329H22.4V22.3996" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.86667" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div><div class="text-text_00  flex h-[28px] w-[28px] items-center justify-center rounded-[4px] transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110  cursor-pointer"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M22.4 14.9329V20.5329C22.4 21.028 22.2033 21.5028 21.8532 21.8529C21.5032 22.2029 21.0284 22.3996 20.5333 22.3996H7.46664C6.97157 22.3996 6.49678 22.2029 6.14671 21.8529C5.79664 21.5028 5.59998 21.028 5.59998 20.5329V7.46628C5.59998 6.97121 5.79664 6.49641 6.14671 6.14634C6.49678 5.79628 6.97157 5.59961 7.46664 5.59961H13.0666M22.4 5.59961L14 13.9996M22.4 5.59961H16.8M22.4 5.59961V11.1996" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.86667" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex flex-col px-[14px] md:max-h-[468px]"><div class="mb-[24px] hidden md:block"><h1 class="text-bg_opacity_100 mb-[12px] text-[24px] font-[500]">春天里</h1><div class="scroll-shadow-wrapper"><div class="scroll-shadow-content hide-scrollbar max-h-[88px] overflow-y-auto" data-top-scroll="false" data-bottom-scroll="true"><p class="text-text_01 text-[14px] leading-[22px]">风格：汪峰式流行摇滚，沧桑沙哑男声，中速 120BPM，情绪励志、走心、坚持、温暖、力量感
配器：电吉他、钢琴、弦乐、鼓、贝斯，编曲饱满有层次，副歌爆发感强
人声：成熟男声，沙哑有故事感，像汪峰那种呐喊又深情的唱法, 新世纪</p></div></div></div><div class="scroll-shadow-wrapper"><div class="scroll-shadow-content hide-scrollbar max-md:max-h-[250px] flex md:flex-1 flex-col overflow-hidden overflow-y-auto" data-top-scroll="false" data-bottom-scroll="true"><p class="text-bg_opacity_85 whitespace-pre-wrap text-[13px] font-[400] leading-[22px] md:text-[15px] md:leading-[28px]">
九四年的我 怀揣一个梦
绿皮车摇晃 奔向南方的风
行李箱压着 年少的沉重
霓虹再璀璨 照不进城中村
 

出租屋很小 灯光也很暗
代码敲到深夜 无人道晚安
周末的公司 是我的港湾
把孤独和迷茫 写成未来答案
 

你放下安稳 跨越千里来相伴
把颠沛流离 换成两个人的暖
日子再艰难 我们不曾回头看
一路跌跌撞撞 一路咬牙撑完
 

还记得那年 春天里
我一无所有 闯在这里
从泥泞小巷 到高楼林立
把汗水 活成勋章的意义
 
如今我站在 春风里
肩上有责任 心中有勇气
两个小天使 是最好的期许
这一路辛苦 都值得 被铭记
 

代码写过几行 青春熬几场
压力像浪潮 拍打我肩膀
家是我的光 也是我的方向
再苦再累 也敢继续往前闯
 

那些艰难的时光 都已成过往
